[URL=http://img37.imageshack.us/i/ugotowned.png/][IMG]http://img37.imageshack.us/img37/9599/ugotowned.png[/img][/URL]
so im definently quiting.. im going to be building a new tehpk-scape im going to work on a couple of things im going to list them below and all the previous features will also stay in the source....
[b]Features...
1. all the features of my old sources. 2. New minigames 3. All skills with custom skill areas 4. competitions 5. 20 % duel tournaments 6. 100 % duel arena 7. 100 % clan wars 8. Castle wars 9. barbarian assualt 10. Custom fist of guthix 11. Over 200 Commands 12. 100 % g maul spec 13. 100 % wildy ditch 14. Funpk 15. more shops 16. D claws 17. Maybe a few quests 18. Working doors that open and close 19. Full magic 20. Anti Spam system 21. 100 % barrows 22. tele tabs 23. Varrock npc spawns 24. Lumbridge npc spawns 25. Falador npc spawns 26. around 30 Jad waves 27. Maybe corporal beast 28. A flamebeed minigame 29. 100 % godwars, that means aviansies, hell hounds, the entire godwars and they will be agressive 30. 100 % glory 31. Custom areas 32. Maybe custom smithing, like smithing future items 33. Maybe Custom woodcutting 34. Clue scrolls 35. Clan chat 36. About 80 % pest control, due to map data might not be able to make full 37. Staff zones 38. Slayer 39. Party room 40. Trading 41. Some of the Grand Exchange content 42. All godsword specs 43. all dragon weapon specials 44. all skillcape emotes 45. Working Mute 46. Highscores ______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________ Please support me in this topic to keep it alive as i am working on the server every day
Thank you for reading and please keep this topic alive..
